# ─── RESEND ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The domain in the From address (info@boostthebeast.com) must be verified
# in the Resend dashboard — https://resend.com/domains — before any real
# emails will be delivered. Until verification is complete, use a sandbox
# sender like "onboarding@resend.dev" to avoid silent failures.
